        <!--Name: the text for the choice. Description: The reward that granted by the story. Storytitle: Flavor text title shown when the story happens (mission finished). Completion: Flavor text shown when the story happens. Imperative: The mission that make the story happens. If a story doesn't need a mission to be finished, it will only have Storytitle and Completion.-->
        <!--Antiquity-->
        <!--Leader Chain-->
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_INIT_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Academic Writing</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_INIT_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Yuni immerses herself in a library, looking for a topic for her new research.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_A_NAME">
            <Text>Study natural science.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_A_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 3 Points in the Great Library Legacy Path.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_A_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_INIT_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_A_COMPLETION">
            <Text>After elaborate experiments and some paperwork, Yuni finishes her new theory and inspired academia to think on a brand new field.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_A_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_B_NAME">
            <Text>Study folk customs.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_B_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Become Suzerain over an Independent Power.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_B_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_INIT_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_B_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Yuni records unique customs of people nearby. These cultural traditions raised interest of her people.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_MISSION_B_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_BREAK_NAME">
            <Text>Go for a humorous novel first.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_BREAK_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_INIT_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Scholarship</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_INIT_COMPLETION">
            <Text>A teacher suggests Yuni to provide financial rewards for excellent students.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Let them make some achievements first.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 6 Points in the Great Library Legacy Path.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_INIT_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Among the best students, a "team of friendship" who excels at study and sociality finally wins the reward after an unreasonable appraisal.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_BREAK_NAME">
            <Text>It's not applicable for me after all.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_A_BREAK_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_INIT_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Artistic Rendering</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_INIT_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Artists love the vocabulary Yuni uses to describe, while engineers can barely understand her.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Ask them to learn what romance is.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Build a Wonder.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_INIT_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>People starts to think if even Yuni's ideas are actually too conservative when they finished an unprecedented great building.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_BREAK_NAME">
            <Text>Repeat with plain and accurate words.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_AQ1_B_BREAK_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward} in all Settlements.</Text>
        </Row>
        <!--Random Events-->
        <!--Exploration-->
        <!--Leader Chain-->
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_INIT_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>In Search of Truths</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_INIT_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Some truths are untouchable by even the best minds, but the process of reaching truths itself is what Yuni wants.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_CHOICE_A_NAME">
            <Text>Research falsehood of this world.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_CHOICE_A_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>Story continues.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_CHOICE_B_NAME">
            <Text>Research developmental psychology.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_CHOICE_B_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>Story continues.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Explosions in School</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Young geniuses are having more and more creative ideas, but sometimes they simply blows up the classroom and leaves a mess.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Allocate them to do something useful.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 10 Specialists.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Well educated specialists shine in every field, in a less explosive way.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_BREAK_NAME">
            <Text>Throw them into a dungeon.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A1_BREAK_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Seeding Innovation</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Some rich investors in the bank want to sponsor for some profitable academic research. They reach out for Yuni to discuss details of the plan.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 3 Points in the Enlightenment Legacy Path.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>New creations mean more revenue. Investors grab much of the latter.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_A2_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Atheism</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_COMPLETION">
            <Text>As an atheist, Yuni never know why many people dedicate themselves to religious rites.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Encourage the people to create arts instead of being superstitious.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 2 Kilns.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Though people don't attend temples less, they do improve their taste of art appreciation a lot.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_BREAK_NAME">
            <Text>Let them go if they like.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B1_BREAK_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Secularisation</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_COMPLETION">
            <Text>As dissent over religious teachings are being constantly expressed, Yuni thinks a chance has come to do something.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 5 Relics.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Yuni collects items called relics and uses them smartly to educate the public.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_EX1_B2_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward} in all Settlements.</Text>
        </Row>
