        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_TRIGGER_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Towards Victory</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_TRIGGER_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Yuni suddenly realizes that the ultimate goal for a civilization is to win a Science Victory. She doesn't really know why she thinks so, but she knows the first step.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 1 Point in the Space Race Legacy Path.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_TRIGGER_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Well begun is half done. Yuni needs to prepare for launching a rocket later.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_child_reward}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_REWARD_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_REWARD_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_BETTER_REWARD_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_A_BETTER_REWARD_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward} and enter a Celebration.</Text>
        </Row>

        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_TRIGGER_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>Retell the History</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_TRIGGER_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Remnants of people long gone are waiting to be unearthed. Yuni wants to be the one to revive their stories so that she can pass legends of these treasures to future generations.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_MISSION_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_MISSION_IMPERATIVE">
            <Text>Have 5 Artifacts.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_MISSION_STORYTITLE">
            <Text>{LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_TRIGGER_STORYTITLE}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_MISSION_COMPLETION">
            <Text>Yuni finds that all Artifacts are created by the gamecore when entering the Modern Age. Anyway, they produce [icon:YIELD_CULTURE] Culture normally.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_MISSION_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_child_reward}</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_REWARD_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_REWARD_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_BETTER_REWARD_NAME">
            <Text>Close.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_LEADER_CHAIN_YUNI_MO1_B_BETTER_REWARD_DESCRIPTION">
            <Text>{1_reward} and enter a Celebration.</Text>
        </Row>
